movie.title: Furry Vengeance
movie.description_intro: Hoping to make enough money through an overseas employer to live comfortably, Real Estate Developer Dan Sanders manages to convince his son, Tyler, and wife, Tammy, to re-locate in a remote corner of Oregon. Tyler does seem content after he meets with lovely Amber, but Tammy is concerned about her husband when he near-hysterically claims that local creatures, including beavers, ravens, bears, fox, etc. have joined forces to sabotage his project.

movies.title: The Witches
movies.summary: Five short stories loosely dealing with the roles of women in society. A superstar actress travels to a mountain resort, only to evoke jealousy from women and lust from men. A woman offers to take an injured man to the hospital. A widowed father and his son seek for a new wife and mother. A man seeks revenge for a woman's honor. A bored housewife tries to explain to her husband that he's not as romantic as he used to be.

movies.title: Christmas in Palm Springs
movies.summary: Jessica has a big presentation in Palm Springs. There are a couple of problems though: her two kids who will do anything to get mom and dad back together again - even if they have to hack mom's phone or pose as a secretary to make sure dad's in Palm Springs too. And father Joe who'll do anything to charm his way back into Jessica's life.

movies.title: Charade
movies.summary: In what's been called 'the best Alfred Hitchcock filn which he didn't direct', a man's thrown of a train, and when the police Trek his wife, it turns out she knew nothing about him - not even his real name. After her are 4 men, who insist she's in possession of a huge amount of money, which they belle to be theirs. If she doesn't give it to them, she'll be killed.
